76561198138109726,Recommended,221640,29299426,Posted: 16 January,all,FolanTheWolfTamer,"I give This review an 11/10, It stole my life.Now if one is to understand how amazing this game truly is, one has to imagine a world filled with puppies and kittens that never grew a day older in their life. Now if you want to experience true tranquility as this, then look no further than this game.I will sum up some of the story, and try not to give spoilers, then I shall list the positives and the negatives in the space below.Super Hexagon was a Game released by Terry Cavanagh in mid 2016 for Android, iOS, Microsoft Windows, Linux, BlackBerry, and Macintosh OS. This game stars a protagonist by the name of Sir Triangalot. He has been burdened with killing his Parents, as punishment for his crimes he was sent to the ever changing maze of hexagons. You pick up as Sir Triangalot in the first twenty seconds of the game, I think that this is a overall plus because it allows you to get into the character through the story without a lot of exposition that inflicts upon your moral views of this character.  The main kicker for this game is the RPG element, you can really get to know Sir Triangalot over the course of this game by the actions that you do over the span of the game, and there are multiple endings.+ This game has amazing graphics that can draw you into the story and atmosphere of the game.+ Even though there is a small amount of songs in Super Hexagon, each and every one is a masterpiece.+ the controls are really tight and simple to figure out.+ Some of the Battles in this game are really challenging. you could spend hours on a boss to finish it completely. This adds a sense of realism in this game.+Also the unique nature of the battles in Super Hexagon set it aside from the majority of gaming genres.+ The story is compelling enough that you wont want to put is down until the end.+ the game is quite long, and it's a great experience all the way through.- The only Negative I can think of for this game is that it may draw you away from your friends and family because it is so good.All in all as I said up top. This game gets a firm 11/10 from me. I highly recomend that you buy this game. ;)"
