76561198127276425,Recommended,221640,9408418,"Posted: 10 March, 2014",all,HardAppleCider,"This game is a must have for everybody that breathes oxygen, and I'd still recommend it to some people that don't.Super Hexagon is a very challenging game and overtaking it feels very rewarding.  It forces you to learn a bit about yourself, the way you think and perceive, and how to know, work within, and expand your own limits.  It will frustrate you, and frustration makes it impossible to play, which means you will get practice in calming yourself down; this is good for you.The game never screws you outright; every single time you die it's entirely your own fault.Super Hexagon is gaming in a primal form made for modern audiences. There's no gear grinding, no character that gets better to make the game easier for the player, no broken mechanics to exploit, or broken builds or strategies to figure out.It's you, and only you, vs the game."
